name: Julienne Bazinet
description: I am a fun, flirty and sexy lady….I love going out and meeting new people…I’m a bit shy and reserved especially around new people….I’m a hopeless romantic and believe that life is much better when you have a companion..I love travelling as well, and I think it would be much better with the love of my life by my side….I’m quite ambitious and a bit stubborn…I’m passionate about love, life and modelling!
